Collect 3 {islandSymbol} to trigger the Island Bonus.{line1complete}
Select 2 squares on each island’s map to reveal coins. If you find the number of coins needed, you travel to the next island to search for more coins.

If you don’t collect enough coins to meet the next island’s goal, you win the previous island’s treasure. If you reach the coins goal on the last island you win that island’s prize.
